                The Scaler School of Technology welcomes students who have completed their Class XII exams in 2024 or earlier, provided they are under the age of 20. This age limit allows us to focus on delivering a tailored educational experience for young individuals who are at a critical stage in their academic journey.
                Admission offers are contingent upon having mathematics as a subject in XII and achieving a mathematics score of above 60%, along with passing XII finals.
                To apply for the program at Scaler School of Technology, please visit our official website at: https://www.scaler.com/school-of-technology/
                  
